{"tid":1795352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪 當 屠 龍 Condom","createTime":"2019-12-24T00:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T00:17:22.000Z","uid":36008,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a79d888240a683aa766668499c8e727ee7f92ba9","tid":1795352,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:17:22.000Z","msg":"和你shop玩爛喇，攞到經濟成果㗎喇<br />\n文宣話去商場已經夠，今晚冇人會食美心。<br />\n和你shop淨係喺度鳩叫、裝修，商場外歌舞昇平，有咩成效？<br />\n<br />\n以前唔批不反，大家會點？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千奇唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n依加個個龜縮入商場，冇勇氣堂堂正正咁向世界展現自己想「光復香港，時代革命」嘅決心，所以轉去打死物，又覺得自己做咗嘢，好似好撚勇咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NeNFV6k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeNFV6k.png&h=32d23302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一係就好似以前咁，冇不反就<ins><strong>千奇唔好去</strong></ins>，一係就收皮。日日喺室內打爆舖頭玻璃呢啲死物，說穿了都係冇咗個勇氣，喺中間唔湯唔水，咁不如唔好搞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n當主流示威者同風向係失去焦點，行動無咗焦點同意義嘅時候，屠龍願意點呀？再升級呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfsA5R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFfsA5R.png&h=d07fc8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋呢？𠵱加屠龍失勢，你哋個個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">口講就話「屠龍係種精神，人人都可以有」。結果仲龜縮過以前，完撚全違反晒屠龍精神，當人condom。</span></strong></span>"}]}